name: True Love Burns
description:
When the god of war met the goddess of beauty, he fell madly in love. Unlike what he did with his other lovers, he decided to woo her. 

He showered her with gifts and compliments until one day Aphrodite finally reciprocated.

"True Love Burns" is part of the "Lovers" series of digital collages that explores the energy of love and its narrative through time.

Passion and war were united forever.
